protein.general_function: Involved in G-protein coupled receptor protein signaling pathway
protein.specific_function: Involved in cannabinoid-induced CNS effects. Acts by inhibiting adenylate cyclase. Could be a receptor for anandamide. Inhibits L-type Ca(2+) channel current. Isoform 2 and isoform 3 have altered ligand binding

go_class.description: cell surface receptor linked signaling pathway
g-protein coupled receptor protein signaling pathway
